<div class="med-sec-label">05 / Optimization Matrix</div>
<section class="med-section">
  <div class="med-inner">
    <h2 class="med-title">TikTok Shop Friction &amp; Optimization Framework</h2>
    
    <table class="dtable">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>To Check</th>
          <th>Data I Review</th>
          <th>Hypothesis I Test</th>
          <th>Action I Prioritize</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>1. Channel</td>
          <td>Link click rate (Link CTR) vs. views in the Seller Center affiliate dashboard.</td>
          <td>High views but low clicks means the content generates interest but the purchase path is broken. High clicks but low purchases means the listing is killing the sale.</td>
          <td>Pin the link in the first comment. Add a verbal CTA in the last 3 seconds of the video. Verify the product is live and correctly mapped in Seller Center.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>2. Expectation</td>
          <td>Comment sentiment and question patterns across the top 5 performing videos.</td>
          <td>The one-star pattern (dry, clumps, doesn't elongate) is due to users applying a specialized Latin lash formula like a generic mascara. The content is failing to set the correct expectation before they buy.</td>
          <td>Add a mandatory line to every creator brief: "designed for straight and thin Latin lashes, here is how to apply it correctly." This single adjustment reduces bad reviews and improves CVR simultaneously.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>3. Listing</td>
          <td>Add-to-cart rate vs. purchase rate in TikTok Shop analytics. Review distribution: 442 one-star reviews visible above the fold.</td>
          <td>Users arrive with high intent, see 442 one-star reviews right at the top, and leave immediately. The social proof is working against the sale, not for it.</td>
          <td>Generate 5-star reviews urgently with a seed wave focused strictly on correct application technique. Add a pinned seller response to the most visible negative reviews explaining the specialized nature of the formula.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>4. Offer Friction</td>
          <td>Checkout drop-off rate in TikTok Shop vs. final price including shipping and taxes.</td>
          <td>The video drives massive impulse intent, but unexpected shipping fees or long delivery estimates at the final step cause immediate cart abandonment.</td>
          <td>Launch an immediate "Free Shipping" coupon for first-time buyers or activate a friction-free logistical bundle directly on the platform.</td>
        </tr>
